{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/github-gists-as-todo-list/","result":{"data":{"site":{"id":"Site","siteMetadata":{"title":"Ayan's Blog"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"af9268a9-bfa1-54bf-9b1a-4127280571fb","excerpt":"Want to use GitHub gists as a todo list? ‚òëÔ∏è Introducing gist-todo-list-action\n(https://github.com/ayan-b/gist-todo-list-action)! Be sure to check the README\nfor‚Ä¶","html":"<p>Want to use GitHub gists as a todo list? ‚òëÔ∏è Introducing [gist-todo-list-action]\n(<a href=\"https://github.com/ayan-b/gist-todo-list-action\">https://github.com/ayan-b/gist-todo-list-action</a>)! Be sure to check the README\nfor more info on how to use it. I will soon write a blog post how I created the\naction.</p>\n<p>This is my submission for <a href=\"https://githubhackathon.com\">GitHub Hackathon</a>!</p>\n<p><strong>Update:</strong></p>\n<p>GitHub declared everyone as a winner üéâü•≥ and I received this nice glass and a\npack of stickers! Here‚Äôs the <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1YL6mjJXGt3-75GejQCubsOvWwtYcGaqbJA7msnsh7Tg/edit#gid=0\">winner list</a>.\nMy submission is on line 159 üòâ.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/blog/static/03b5eddb24436afd75c5a0adacfee3da/c83bb/github-hackathon-glass.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"GitHub Hackathon Glass\"\n        title=\"GitHub Hackathon Glass\"\n        src=\"/blog/static/03b5eddb24436afd75c5a0adacfee3da/1c72d/github-hackathon-glass.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/blog/static/03b5eddb24436afd75c5a0adacfee3da/a80bd/github-hackathon-glass.jpg 148w,\n/blog/static/03b5eddb24436afd75c5a0adacfee3da/1c91a/github-hackathon-glass.jpg 295w,\n/blog/static/03b5eddb24436afd75c5a0adacfee3da/1c72d/github-hackathon-glass.jpg 590w,\n/blog/static/03b5eddb24436afd75c5a0adacfee3da/a8a14/github-hackathon-glass.jpg 885w,\n/blog/static/03b5eddb24436afd75c5a0adacfee3da/fbd2c/github-hackathon-glass.jpg 1180w,\n/blog/static/03b5eddb24436afd75c5a0adacfee3da/c83bb/github-hackathon-glass.jpg 4608w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/blog/static/f1ab64bee5004cae19872de77488e2ac/c83bb/github-hackathon-stickers-pack.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"GitHub Hackathon Stickers Pack\"\n        title=\"GitHub Hackathon Stickers Pack\"\n        src=\"/blog/static/f1ab64bee5004cae19872de77488e2ac/1c72d/github-hackathon-stickers-pack.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/blog/static/f1ab64bee5004cae19872de77488e2ac/a80bd/github-hackathon-stickers-pack.jpg 148w,\n/blog/static/f1ab64bee5004cae19872de77488e2ac/1c91a/github-hackathon-stickers-pack.jpg 295w,\n/blog/static/f1ab64bee5004cae19872de77488e2ac/1c72d/github-hackathon-stickers-pack.jpg 590w,\n/blog/static/f1ab64bee5004cae19872de77488e2ac/a8a14/github-hackathon-stickers-pack.jpg 885w,\n/blog/static/f1ab64bee5004cae19872de77488e2ac/fbd2c/github-hackathon-stickers-pack.jpg 1180w,\n/blog/static/f1ab64bee5004cae19872de77488e2ac/c83bb/github-hackathon-stickers-pack.jpg 4608w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><em>The following text is taken from the project readme.</em></p>\n<h2>Features</h2>\n<h3>Before</h3>\n<p>Create a Todo List in a GitHub Gist (following the\n<a href=\"https://help.github.com/en/github/managing-your-work-on-github/about-task-lists#creating-task-lists\">task list syntax</a>)\nand create a list, and check the tasks you have done off during the day.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ayan-b/gist-todo-list-action/master/images/before-todo.png\" alt=\"before todo\"></p>\n<h3>After</h3>\n<p>After midnight your done tasks will be transferred to the done list. In this\nway you will have a history of your list!</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Todo</th>\n<th>Done</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ayan-b/gist-todo-list-action/master/images/after-todo.png\" alt=\"after todo\"></td>\n<td><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ayan-b/gist-todo-list-action/master/images/done.png\" alt=\"done\"></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2>Usage</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>First create two gists from <a href=\"https://gist.github.com\">https://gist.github.com</a>, namely <code class=\"language-text\">todo</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">done</code>.</li>\n<li>Add file <code class=\"language-text\">todo.md</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">done.md</code> to them respectively. The file content should\nbe a single header <code class=\"language-text\"># Todo</code> and <code class=\"language-text\"># Done</code> respectively.</li>\n<li>Generate a new personal access token with gist scope from\nhere: <a href=\"https://github.com/settings/tokens/new\">https://github.com/settings/tokens/new</a>.</li>\n<li>Fork this repository. Note that if you want to use GitHub Action from market place,\nyou don‚Äôt need to fork this repository. See <a href=\"#using-with-github-action\">this</a> for more instruction.</li>\n<li>\n<p>Add the gist IDs as <code class=\"language-text\">TODO_GIST</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">DONE_GIST</code> and the personal access token as\n<code class=\"language-text\">GH_TOKEN</code> to your repository secrets: <code class=\"language-text\">https://github.com/&lt;your_username&gt;/&lt;repository_name&gt;/settings/secrets</code>.\nIt will look something like this:</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ayan-b/gist-todo-list-action/master/images/secrets.png\" alt=\"secrets.jpg\"></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Gist ID is the part of the URL after your username. For example the gist ID\nof this gist <code class=\"language-text\">https://gist.github.com/ayan-b/1b44e52eifj09bc75c914f6fedf95304</code>\nis <code class=\"language-text\">1b44e52eifj09bc75c914f6fedf95304</code>.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n<li>Now you have your todo list using GitHub gist!</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Optional</strong>: Change the time of <a href=\"https://github.com/ayan-b/gist-todo-list-action/blob/master/.github/workflows/update-list.yml\">cron job</a>\nin the workflow file according to your time zone so that the todo and done\nlist update exactly at midnight (and not at UTC midnight)!</p>\n<p>Here‚Äôs one for IST time zone (UTC +5:30). Note the use of <code class=\"language-text\">TIME_ZONE</code> environment\nvariable and the change in cron job.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"yaml\"><pre class=\"language-yaml\"><code class=\"language-yaml\"><span class=\"token key atrule\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Update Todo List IST\n\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">on</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">push</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">branches</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span> master <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">pull_request</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">branches</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span> master <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">schedule</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> <span class=\"token key atrule\">cron</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"30 5 * * *\"</span>  <span class=\"token comment\"># 0 + time zone difference time</span>\n\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">jobs</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">build</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">runs-on</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> ubuntu<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>latest\n\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">steps</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> <span class=\"token key atrule\">uses</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> actions/checkout@v2\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> <span class=\"token key atrule\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Set up Python 3.8\n      <span class=\"token key atrule\">uses</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> actions/setup<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>python@v1\n      <span class=\"token key atrule\">with</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        <span class=\"token key atrule\">python-version</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">3.8</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> <span class=\"token key atrule\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Install dependencies\n      <span class=\"token key atrule\">run</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">|</span><span class=\"token scalar string\">\n        python -m pip install --upgrade pip\n        pip install -r requirements.txt</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> <span class=\"token key atrule\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Lint with flake8\n      <span class=\"token key atrule\">run</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">|</span><span class=\"token scalar string\">\n        pip install flake8\n        # stop the build if there are Python syntax errors or undefined names\n        flake8 . --count --select=E9,F63,F7,F82 --show-source --statistics\n        # exit-zero treats all errors as warnings.\n        flake8 . --count --exit-zero --max-complexity=10 --max-line-length=79 --statistics</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> <span class=\"token key atrule\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Update todo list\n      <span class=\"token key atrule\">run</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">|</span><span class=\"token scalar string\">\n        python3 construct_todo.py</span>\n      <span class=\"token key atrule\">env</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        <span class=\"token key atrule\">GH_TOKEN</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> $<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> secrets.GH_TOKEN <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        <span class=\"token key atrule\">TODO_GIST</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> $<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> secrets.TODO_GIST <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        <span class=\"token key atrule\">DONE_GIST</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> $<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> secrets.DONE_GIST <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        <span class=\"token key atrule\">TIME_ZONE</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Asia/Kolkata\"</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># IST</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Note that you can use docker as well in the last step (<code class=\"language-text\">Update todo list</code>) as done\nin the <a href=\"https://github.com/ayan-b/gist-todo-list-action/blob/master/.github/workflows/update-list.yml\"><code class=\"language-text\">update-list.yml</code></a> file. But it will\nbe slower. You can also omit the <code class=\"language-text\">Lint with flake8</code> step.</p>\n<h3>Using with GitHub action</h3>\n<p>If you want to use GitHub action, your workflow yaml file will look something like\nthis (be sure to change the version to the latest one):</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"yaml\"><pre class=\"language-yaml\"><code class=\"language-yaml\"><span class=\"token key atrule\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Update Todo List IST\n\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">on</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">push</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">branches</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span> master <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">pull_request</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">branches</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span> master <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">schedule</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> <span class=\"token key atrule\">cron</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"30 5 * * *\"</span>  <span class=\"token comment\"># 0 + time zone difference time</span>\n\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">jobs</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">build</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">runs-on</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> ubuntu<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>latest\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">steps</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> <span class=\"token key atrule\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Todo List using GitHub Gist\n      <span class=\"token key atrule\">uses</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> ayan<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>b/gist<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>todo<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>list<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>action@0.1.0\n      <span class=\"token key atrule\">env</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        <span class=\"token key atrule\">GH_TOKEN</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> $<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> secrets.GH_TOKEN <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        <span class=\"token key atrule\">TODO_GIST</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> $<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> secrets.TODO_GIST <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        <span class=\"token key atrule\">DONE_GIST</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> $<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> secrets.DONE_GIST <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        <span class=\"token key atrule\">TIME_ZONE</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Asia/Kolkata\"</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># IST</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"GitHub Action - Use GitHub Gists as a Todo List","date":"September 04, 2020","description":"Gist-todo-list-action - My submission for GitHub Hackathon!"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/github-gists-as-todo-list/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/GSoC-2020-Report/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"GSoC 2020 Report: Upgrade and Fix tvb-gdist C++ Library"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/latex-resume-website-github-action/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"GitHub Action - Create a LaTeX Resume and Website from a Single Data File"}}}}}